Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好暖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 振作啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能睡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.26,0:01:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是登山女生啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我已经不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是你一个人活下去也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.19,0:01:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登顶成功 「女子力」升级
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人去当大众情人咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大众情人~ 大众情人~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向你等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好一起攀登回忆中的山峰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷 开着空调就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫雪村葵 今年高一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直是室内派 但最近也开始对登山感兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 冬天的富士山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 竟然丢下别人只顾自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向你太绝情了 什么大众情人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己做的梦 找我抱怨也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平时不攒人品 才会反映到我的梦里的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你有理 算你有理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还梦到回忆中的山峰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我 要支帐篷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是日向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算我的发小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我进入驴友圈的就是这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住帐篷吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:37.97,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合目：登山进度 一般来说从山脚到山顶共分十合（也有一些山有十以上的合）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帐篷能一下子住四个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看它叠起来很小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支起来很宽敞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快支起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人能支起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻松松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这边按着 你把骨架穿进套管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,套管？骨架？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是套管 把骨架穿进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来再穿一根进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把骨架的两头穿进扣环
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣环是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加最后一把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的帐篷 支起来也不难嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说我为什么在日向家院子里支帐篷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去山里野营？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约上可可娜酱和小枫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去野营啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好！好主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 饭还没好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和朋友约好去野营
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野营？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着吃的去野炊 再在帐篷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友去野营？ 只有女孩子去？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去日向家住一晚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 日向的爸爸也在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别给人家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 我们就在日向家的院子里野营了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 我们开始打桩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(785,640)}Peg
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打狗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是Pug 沙皮狗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Peg可是桩子、钉子的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是桩子就说桩子 装什么装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,略微朝外侧倾斜 要钉到底哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把绳索钩在地桩上 固定住帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大功告成！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 搭得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好宽敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把手脚伸开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可娜酱！小枫学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们也是驴友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是比我们高一年级的小枫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光在学校是学姐 在登山方面也是我们的先辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个 是中学生 可可娜酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哇 好棒的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子力可高了 是个治愈系女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买晚饭的材料来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫学姐这样做过饭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算做过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米淘好之后 先在水中浸一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天用的是碳烤炉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾的是火候掌控不到「先弱后强」的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么「先弱后强」？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古人形容做饭火候的俗语哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「孩子饿哭了也不能打开锅盖」！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖子被顶开的话就加上重物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到米汤不往外溢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来做咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锅里放少许油 把洋葱煎到金黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金黄色？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来依次加入土豆 胡萝卜 肉 再翻炒一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后加水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮一段时间之后 撇净浮泡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把咖喱块煮化之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 再加上这些风味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…和咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加进去之后超好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米饭也做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米饭稍微有点焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锅巴好香！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱也做得好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但完全吃不出来巧克力味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃出来就不叫风味啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有好多 可以添碗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放那么多蛋黄酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放的还算少呢 登山的时候需要卡路里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便放下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 日向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着心跳上升！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向好过分！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只管自己洗澡 都不帮忙收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵也去洗啊 好舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去快去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在别人家洗澡 总有些拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没伸开手脚泡澡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡得很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 人间天堂 人间天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 小枫学姐这样不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫学姐 快穿衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉抱歉 坏习惯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可娜酱 不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来觉得挺宽敞 但四个人进来就显得挤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向你再往那边点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登山小屋还有比这更挤的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旺季简直是大通铺 人挤人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挤得跟早高峰的电车一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样也能睡着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都累坏了 睡得可香了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再做荷兰蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用好多黄油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着就想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我也做做看 火腿蛋松饼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们玩单词接龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只许说山名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等 刚才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.88,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日语中没有鼻音ん(n)开头的单词 所以说音读「山(san)」结尾的就算输了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高尾山！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:07.78,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高尾山 第一季中介绍过的山 位于东京郊外 感兴趣的同学请观看第一季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐山！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:12.44,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐山 位于青森县下总半岛中部的火山 海拔878米 以温泉众多闻名\N是一座与山岳信仰和佛教信仰渊源深厚的灵山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉韦厄火山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时候也不早了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情感热线时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情感？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有四个女生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从小葵说起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在喜欢谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又来这套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟米田君后来如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:29.20,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米田君 第一季故事中小葵幼年时的绯闻男友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么扯到小学的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先说说你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果非要说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的是山哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可可娜酱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜欢的人吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对梦马君不能自拔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦马君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:46.75,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦马君 本故事的舞台琦玉县饭能市的吉祥物（之一…）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸有点长 又毛茸茸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:10:35.18,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日语歌曲『岳人の歌』 词曲作者不详 是日本歌唱登山者的名曲之一

Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}星が降るあのコル グリセードで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}あの人は来るかしら 花をくわえて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}アルプスの恋唄 心ときめくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}懐かしの岳人 やさしかの君 やさしかの君

Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}踏着皑皑白雪 穿过满天星空的圈谷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}嘴里衔着鲜花的他 会不会来寻觅我的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}阿尔卑斯的恋曲 让人怦然心动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}回忆中的登山家 是温柔的你 是温柔的你…

Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦马
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向！要振作啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会丢下你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 我吃得好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放弃啊 马上就到山顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起当大众情…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦家不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 日向好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵起得好早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由得就想起来 小时候我们一起看的日出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果从富士山看 一定会更美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士山么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起野营 真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要到真正的山里野营呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:04.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 不思議と どうしてかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:12.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミが笑うと 心の奥いつもキラリまたたく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's little step! 一歩ずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's feel skip! 一緒にねっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:30.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気がつけば 夢中になってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:35.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「そういうコトあるよね」って言ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:41.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キュッと手と手つないだら 伝わる ぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:46.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこにでも行けちゃう気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:52.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tin-Ton-Tan 踏み出した瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:58.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界がパノラマみたいにひらけたの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:03.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile こんな空の広さ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:09.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人きりじゃ きっと気づけなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:14.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 笑顔こだましてる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:22.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸に広がる やさしい うれしい あたらしい予感たち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:27.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一歩一歩進んで行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:04.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 多么不可思议 是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:12.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你微笑 心中就像繁星般闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's little step! 一步一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's feel skip! 一起来呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:30.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来 已经沉浸其中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:35.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你对我说 「常有的事情！」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:41.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺着紧握的双手 传来你的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:46.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛能走到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:52.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叮 咚 铛 迈出一步的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:58.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界像全景照片一样展现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:03.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 如此广阔的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:09.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只身一人 一定不会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:14.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 笑容在回响
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:22.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满内心的温柔和喜悦 还有新的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:27.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步一步往前走吧！